0) Download and install elasticsearch from www.elasticsearch.org and check that elasticsearch is in your PATH
1) Install pu branch of Invenio and his corresponding demo-site.
2) Clone the project from github
3) cdvirtualenv
4) mkdir src; cd src
5) ~/src/git-new-workdir ~/src/elasticsearch_view es-view
6) cd es-view
7) pip install -e .
8) Check that PACKAGES contain "invenio_demosite", "elasticsearch_view.modules.*", else set it via inveniomanage
9) foreman start

If you're lucky go to http://localhost:4000/es
